# Xrefs — reverse-lookup a Go symbol

Run `gofasta xrefs <Symbol> --json`. Symbol can be a bare name
(`UserController`), a package-qualified function
(`app/services.UserService`), or a method
(`app/services.UserService.Create`).

Report the definition location and every reference site (file,
line, enclosing function). If the result is `AMBIGUOUS_SYMBOL`,
ask the user which package they meant.

Use this before renaming a function or changing a signature.
